data.title: Dream, or The Simian Maid by S. Fowler Wright: Good Hardcover (1931) 1st Edition
data.meta_description: 1st Edition - Hardcover - George G. Harrap & Company, London - 1931 - Condition: Good - First edition, 1st printing in red cloth with spine titled in black, cover ruled in blind. Association copy - Forey Ackerman. London; George G. Harrap & Company (1931), 251 pages. A Good copy with bumped corners, slightly soiled front and rear boards, sun fading to spine.Cracked hinges, rear joint torn, front free endpaper has Forey Ackerman's inked writing and stickers. No jacket. - Dream, or The Simian Maid
